wikipedia_page.main: Susan Jane le Jeune d'Allegeershecque,  (née Miller; born 29 April 1963) is a British diplomat who, most recently, served as British High Commissioner to Canada from 2017-2021. She previously served as British Ambassador to Austria from 2012 to 2016.

Susannah Clare Goshko  is a British civil servant in Her Majesty's Diplomatic Service. She presently serves as the British High Commissioner to Canada, replacing Susan le Jeune d'Allegeershecque on September 7, 2021.
